        "subject": "LU-6175 ha: add health_check routine to the MDS, MGS and OSD",
        "message": "LU-6175 ha: add health_check routine to the MDS, MGS and OSD\n\nPatch adds obd_health_check() methods in MDS and MGS to check\nptlrpc services health like OST does. Patch adds also health_check()\nroutine directly to OSD to check it is mounted and is not read-only.\n\nThis patch is back-ported from the following one:\nLustre-commit: f3e49e66608a20ac1b006b5e4202ad8ad88c1979\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/13558\n\nSigned-off-by: Mikhail Pershin <mike.pershin@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I215134599677dfac5dfc5ae743eba3f28671839b\n"
